B6pcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cca3fc7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/baby/yjnb3j.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"佢29完 我地1號sex 佢10-13號有假經血 今日3/10仲未黎m"},{"pid":"9a1c645ae6ff45070759717cd093df9440e0e3e9","tid":839994,"uid":214056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"陰莖勃起"},{"pid":"d64ce3f39f22378ec0f8216367018bb606117705","tid":839994,"uid":213119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0dc4d853a7e9cc4ce160321179a6f43eded5544","tid":839994,"uid":192816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53e7644ef8317a155bce851a18bd11c2d31400dc","tid":839994,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d4d52373a6e1c560cdaf7e3c6b8a55335c094c","tid":839994,"uid":192816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"佢話比m量小 但都要用m巾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"如何正確區分陰道出血是着床懷孕還是來大姨媽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1、顏色區分<br />\n<br />\n大姨媽的血是紅色的，而着床出血的顏色是粉色的或者褐色的，一般着床出血不會出現紅色的。<br />\n<br />\n2、量的區分<br />\n<br />\n着床出血顏色淡，量也很少，不會出現增多現象，而大姨媽來了，剛開始量少，慢慢會增多，而且會有血塊凝結，這些很好區分。<br />\n<br />\n3、周期的區分<br />\n<br />\n大姨媽的周期正常是持續4-7天，剛開始少，慢慢增多，再慢慢減少，而着床出血一般會斷斷續續，時間也短，一般在1-2天就結束了。<br />\n<br />\n4、肚子疼的情況<br />\n<br />\n來大姨媽可能由於痛經會有腹痛現象，而着床也會有輕微腹痛，但程度比來大姨媽輕多了，也不會出現腹痛加劇的現象。如果你實在確認不了，不如直接去醫院檢查或者買早早孕試紙檢測，這是最保險的方法啦!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/baby/yjnb3j.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fbaby%2Fyjnb3j.html&d=TpGw%2FtpkxdTkwnVWdDB6pcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cca3fc7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/baby/yjnb3j.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"佢29完 我地1號sex 佢10-13號有假經血 今日3/10仲未黎m"},"cited